		//		Method to add an reference map entry for an item and attribute.
		// description:
		//		Method to add an reference map entry for an item and attribute.
		// refItem:
		//		The item that is referenced.
		// parentItem:
		//		The item that holds the new reference to refItem.
		// attribute:
		//		The attribute on parentItem that contains the new reference.

